The Keiser Report  No. 129
= Max Keiser and Stacy Herbert =
Tuesday, 15 March 2011


[sebaygo1]


Supermassive $30 Billion Black Hole

This week Max Keiser and co-host, Stacy Herbert, report on 30 billion black holes, food price riots and toppling the tyrants in the UK. 

In the second half of the show, Max talks to Richard Heinberg of the Post Carbon Institute about the Goldilocks Syndrome and the market response to resource scarcity. <a href="
http://www.postcarbon.org/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.postcarbon.org/</a>
